{"title":"2001年的春天","authors":["王怀让"],"dates":[{"year":2001,"month":1,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"2001年的春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王怀让"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"2001年的春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"2001年的春天来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和往年一样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它是以迎春花为仪仗队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"由柳条儿和杨絮儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"簇拥着走来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一步一步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一步都是芬芳或者鲜艳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"2001年的春天来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和往年不同，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往年的春天只是迈过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬天的门坎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而它却还要迈过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新世纪的门坎和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新千年的门坎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它的步伐很新鲜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一步一步走着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一步都是雷声或雨点。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"2001年的春天来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着人民日报"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新年献辞的方块字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一步一步走来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是社论的声音。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"2001年的春天来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踩着黄河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚刚解冻的冰凌块"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一步一步走来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是高亢的音符。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天的雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好大的一场雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一场春天的雪哟！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天的雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和冬天的雪不同："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬天的雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是从天上落下来的；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天的雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像梦一样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从我的心中飘来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好大的一场雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一场春天的雪哟！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天的雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和冬天的雪不同："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬天的雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给我戴上很重很重的帽子；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天的雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像傣家的泼水节，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让人想到轻松和痛快。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好大的一场雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一场春天的雪哟！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天的雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和冬天的雪不同："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬天的雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给我戴上很厚很厚的手套；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天的雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像六一儿童节，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让人感到灵巧和跳跃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好大的一场雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一场春天的雪哟！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天的雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和冬天的雪不同："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬天的雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是有声的凛冽；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天的雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是无声的温馨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滋润着油菜花开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也滋润着工地上的新楼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一层一层地拔节……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高速公路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开春，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又一条高速公路开工！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们为它修筑厚实的路基，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路基是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个刚刚过去的世纪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开春，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又一条高速公路开工！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们铺设了平坦的路面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路面是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个刚刚到来的千年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们用高速公路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把中国的版图扎起来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"设计时速——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高速公路上汽车跑多快，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国就跑多快！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们用高速公路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把时间和时间焊接！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竖起路标——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"入口：繁忙的今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出口：繁荣的未来！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}